sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Admin User
    participant A as Server A (Consumer)
    participant B as Server B (Origin)

    Note over Admin,B: Setup Phase

    Admin->>A: POST /api/v1/federation/peers<br/>{server_url, api_key}
    A->>B: GET /api/v1/federation/manifest
    B-->>A: {server_id, server_name, catalog_count}
    A-->>Admin: Peer added (server_id)

    Note over A,B: Catalog Sync (periodic or manual)

    A->>B: GET /api/v1/federation/catalog?page=1
    B-->>A: {items: [...], total, page}
    loop For each item
        A->>A: Upsert remote_media_cache
        A->>B: GET /api/v1/federation/media/{slug}/thumbnail
        B-->>A: thumbnail binary (WebP)
        A->>A: Cache to storage/federation_cache/{server_id}/thumbnails/
    end
    A->>A: Update peer status = online, last_synced_at

    Note over Admin,B: User Browsing (on Server A)

    participant User as End User

    User->>A: GET /federation/{server_id}
    A->>A: Query remote_media_cache
    A-->>User: Catalog page (cached thumbnails)

    User->>A: GET /federation/{server_id}/media/{slug}
    A-->>User: Detail page

    User->>A: GET /federation/{server_id}/media/{slug}/image.webp
    alt Content cached locally
        A-->>User: Serve from federation_cache
    else Not cached
        A->>B: GET /api/v1/federation/media/{slug}/content
        B-->>A: Media binary
        A->>A: Cache locally
        A-->>User: Proxied content
    end
